This airy apartment is bright and welcoming. Just a 5-minute walk from Braga's historic center, it is close to the main access routes to the city and the city's bus station. It is located on the 1st floor, without an elevator. Parking is free on the street.

It is fully furnished and equipped, so you don't have to spend any extra money. It has two bedrooms with double beds and a full bathroom. The kitchen is equipped with all the essentials, such as a fridge, microwave, stove, oven and coffee machine. The apartment also has a washing machine and flat-screen TV in the living room. In addition, there is an outdoor balcony accessible from the living room and kitchen.

accommodation_offer.title: Bright 1 bedroom apartment near Braga Cathedral
accommodation_offer.description:
The On the Square Flat apartment is located in the heart of the city, right in the historic center of Braga. With easy access to the main roads and public transport, it is a comfortable and welcoming apartment, close to cafés, restaurants, local shops, a market and a fruit shop. It is located on the 3rd floor, without an elevator, and parking is free on the street.

It is fully furnished and equipped, so you don't have to spend any extra money. It has a bedroom with a double bed, air conditioning and a closet. The kitchen is equipped with all the essential utensils for everyday life (hob, oven, microwave, coffee machine and washing machine). The dining and living area, in open space with the kitchen, also has a flat-screen TV, sofa bed and Wi-Fi.
